  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll get a hot and cold buffet with lots of options. Dinner will be a four-course buffet. There's also a weekly gala dinner included. The hotel also provides early meals for children which are available from 6.30pm.</p>
<p>Please note, the hotel requests that no shorts of flip flops are worn at dinner.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
