  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Splendid Palace is in a fantastic location over-looking the lake. It's surrounded by lemon groves and is just a short walk from Limone's historic city centre.</p>
<h2>Panoramic view of Lake Garda</h2>
<p>If you fancy a walk or cycle during the day, you're not far from the lakeside cycleway. The path's suspended above the lake at points giving you another chance to take in the beautiful scenery. One of our favourite things to do before dinner is to grab a seat on the terrace that overlooks the lake and mountains and order a glass of prosecco. You don't want to miss these views!</p>
<h2>Tuck into tasty Italian dinners</h2>
<p>We love the array of food at the dinner-time buffet here. There are endless options of salads, pasta, roasts, hot dishes that can all be topped off with a fantastic selection of desserts.</p>]]></description>
