  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are around 14m² and sleep up to two people. They have a terrace and are located at pool level, looking out onto the pool area. </p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms with lake views </strong>are around 15m² and sleep up to two people. They have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are smaller at about 12m² and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for sole use </strong>are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Please request double or twin beds at the time of booking</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Mini-fridge</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of €2 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
